description:
In Part 4 of the NBA trade deadline podcast, The Ringer's Bill Simmons is joined by Kevin O'Connor, Wosny Lambre, J. Kyle Mann, and Rob Mahoney to give out their winners and losers, including Kevin Durant, Steve Nash, the Bucks, Russell Westbrook, and more!

Host: Bill Simmons
Guests: Kevin O'Connor, Wosny Lambre, Rob Mahoney, and J. Kyle Mann
Producers: Kyle Crichton and Steve Ceruti
